[[File:Flag of Transcaucasian SFSR.svg|thumb|288px|Flag of the Transcaucasian Soviet Federative Socialist Republic]]

The '''flag of the Transcaucasian Socialist Federative Soviet Republic''' ({{lang-ru|Флаг Закавка́зской СФСР}}, ''Flag Zakavkázskoj SFSR'') was adopted by the [[Transcaucasian Socialist Federative Soviet Republic]] in the 1930s.

Prior to this, the flag was red with the [[Cyrillic script|Cyrillic]] characters ''ЗСФСР'' in gold in a sans-serif font.

