The '''Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Gokwe''' ({{lang-la|Gokven(sis)}}) is a suffragan diocese in the city of [[Gokwe]] in the ecclesiastical province of Harare in Zimbabwe.
==History== * June 17, 1991: Established as Diocese of Gokwe from [[Diocese of Hwange]]
==Bishops== # [[Michael Dixon Bhasera]] (17 June 1991 – 9 February 1999) # [[Ángel Floro Martínez]], [[Instituto Español de San Francisco Javier para Misiones Extranjeras|IEME]] (15 October 1999 – 28 April 2017) # [[Rudolf Nyandoro]] (29 April 2017 – )
