'''Themisonium''' was a city in the late [[Roman province]] of [[Phrygia|Phrygia Pacatiana Prima]]. 

Its [[bishopric]] was a [[suffragan]] of [[Laodicea on the Lycus|Laodicea in Phrygia]], the capital and [[metropolitan see]] of the province.<ref>''Annuario Pontificio 2013'' (Libreria Editrice Vaticana, 2013, {{ISBN|978-88-209-9070-1}}), p. 986</ref><ref>{{CathEncy|wstitle=Themisonium}}</ref>

