The '''Torre Lúgano''' is a residential building in [[Benidorm]], [[Spain]] and measured 148 meters in height.<ref>[http://www.emporis.com/building/torrelugano-benidorm-spain Torre Lugano, Benidorm | Building 189845 | EMPORIS]</ref> It is the third highest building in Benidorm, and the [[List of tallest buildings in Spain|ninth tallest building in Spain]].<ref>[http://www.roundtownnews.com/index.php?option=com_k2&view=itemlist&task=tag&tag=tallest&Itemid=219 Rugby – Free Weekly newspaper on the Costa Blanca, Costa Calida with all the Local News, Sport and Major Stories and Events – Round Town News]</ref><ref>[http://elpais.com/diario/2010/06/15/cvalenciana/1276629478_850215.html One of the giants of Benidorm suffers all kinds of damage | Print Edition | COUNTRY]</ref>

